<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200915/e610b2bf8e1742b091531772b02f1de2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">故事易懂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">分镜流畅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人物造型成熟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">景别应用丰富</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">色彩搭配舒适效果强</p>
